metadata.name: MATTIE - OTB #1
metadata.description:
MATTIE is a mirror.  
A watch-person over the keys to liberation. 

MATTIE guides listening & viewing experience through self-taught modalities of vocalization, lyrical self-inquiry, harmonic dynamics, unconventional instrumentation, movement, meditation, and performance art practice.

MATTIE's "Out This Bitch" series is a collaboration with Dallas Texas-based art director Tramaine Townsend & composer Black Taffy.
